      "content": "im sitting here just looking at the wall and thinking... i don't think i actually belong here. like, not in this world. everything feels so loud and heavy and nothing makes sense. it feels like i'm just an alien pretending to be human and i'm failing at it. does that ever happen to you? like just feeling completely disconnected from everything?",
